<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ website_name }} - Configuration Drift Demo</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .status {
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-ok {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        }
        .status-info {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            color: #0c5460;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
        }
        .monitoring-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        code {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 2px 5px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>{{ website_name }}</h1>
        <div class="status status-ok">
            ‚úÖ System Status: Configuration Drift Detection Platform - DESIRED STATE ACTIVE
        </div>
        
        <div class="monitoring-info">
            <h3>üìä Monitoring Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Hostname:</strong> {{ ansible_hostname }}</p>
            <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</p>
            <p><strong>Web Server:</strong> {{ webserver | upper }}</p>
            <p><strong>Last Configuration:</strong> {{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>About This Platform</h2>
        <p>This is a demonstration of Configuration Drift Detection and Self-Remediation.</p>
        <p>The system continuously monitors for unauthorized changes and automatically restores the desired state.</p>
        
        <h2>Health Endpoints</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="{{ health_check_path }}">{{ health_check_path }}</a> - Health check</li>
            <li><code>/var/log/{{ webserver }}/</code> - Access and error logs</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="status status-info">
            ‚ÑπÔ∏è Desired State: <code>{{ state_checksum_file }}</code> contains expected configuration checksums
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p><small>Ansible Managed - {{ ansible_managed }}</small></p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
